t2042.text: I’m not sure if I’m an arsehole for saying this but it’s a bit sad that this is what brought them out of the woodwork. Oh and mum is pissed because we don’t think Colin’s wife Vikky is coming to the funeral. The rest of his family are but she isn’t.

t2043.text: She died pretty much as soon as we couldn’t be at her bedside 24 seven. We have family who we have never met before getting in contact. Dad’s cousin Cindy keeps calling because apparently she exists. Who even are half these people?

t2044.text: We all stayed for as long as we could but eventually, we had to go back to work. Please don’t hate us. We didn’t have any other options. We stayed for as long as we could. We still visited as much as we could but we couldn’t come as often because work.

t2045.text: They said dad’s brother Colin wouldn’t make it in time because he lived on the other side of the country. He had to fly in and they thought she would die before his plane landed. He made it and stayed for a few days.
